      <title>全球基金对中国银行债务的投资降温，流入量减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/global-funds-cool-on-china-bank-debt-with-inflows-shrinking</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人民币走强以及汇率干预可能减少，流行的基于掉期的交易吸引力降低，8月份全球基金对中国银行券的购买量突然放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/global-funds-cool-on-china-bank-debt-with-inflows-shrinking</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 03:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
